  tomatoes-1.55-r1.ebuild:
  avoid prestripping binaries (bug #137672) - patch from Tristan Heaven

  13 Apr 2006; Chris Gianelloni <wolf31o2@gentoo.org> -tomatoes-1.55.ebuild:
